text: "Jesse" is a 1980 song by Carly Simon and is the lead single from her 9th studio album Come Upstairs. It went to number 4 in Australia, number 11 in the United States and number 12 in Canada. ==Track listing== ;7" single * "Jesse" – 4:15 * "Stardust" – 4:13 == References == Category:1980 songs Category:Pop rock songs Category:Carly Simon songs
